{
  "stem": "14724.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one eve-- one night in the middle of the winter, my father must have smelled smoke and went outside and saw the synagogue aflame, with us in it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he managed to get all of us out-- and my mother, again, pregnant and a babe in arms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there we could see a group of Nazi youths with bricks in their hands.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were determined to exterminate us as well as the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The synagogue burned down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in the whatever it was, with the fires going and the people shouting, some Jewish-- some non-Jewish people got us away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were in our nightclothes and no shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they hid us in an ice cellar, which in those days was a hollowed-out hill filled with ice.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE] fridges.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were-- these people who lived in the big house put us into the ice cellar when there was virtually mass hysteria because they couldn't find us and they wanted to kill us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we knew they wanted to kill us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But the rest of the day-- of that night is a complete blank.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Actually, it was only four years ago that I saw this-- the ice cellar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I met the daughter of the people who saved us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, in this mass hysteria they smuggled us away from the fire, these non-Jewish people, and they hid us in the ice cellar--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--until next day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by next day, of course, the hysteria, which-- when a group of Hitler youths get together, they wind one another up, as we now say.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's just one hysteric mob.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all they wanted to do was kill us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was they synagogue and us, nobody else involved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Five children two grown-ups-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
